comment7.text=\n\ Returns\ the\ current\ top\ state\ without\ removing\ it.\n\ Returns\ null\ if\ the\ stack\ is\ empty.\n\ Useful\ when\ you\ need\ to\ call\ a\ method\ specific\ to\ a\ known\ state\ type.\n
